00038 Entree& Saturation_constant::readOn(Entree& is)
00039 {
00040   Param param(que_suis_je());
00041   param.ajouter("Tsat", &tsat_,Param::REQUIRED);
00042   param.ajouter("Psat", &psat_,Param::REQUIRED);
00043   param.ajouter("Lvap", &lvap_);
00044   param.ajouter("Hlsat", &hls_);
00045   param.ajouter("Hvsat", &hvs_);
00046   param.lire_avec_accolades_depuis(is);
00047 // verifications hlsat/hvsat/lvap
00048   const int i = (lvap_ > 0) + (hls_ > 0) + (hvs_ > 0);
00049   if (i != 2) Process::exit(que_suis_je() + " Please give 2 properties among {Lvap, Hlsat, Hvsat}");
00050   if (lvap_ > 0 && hls_ > 0) hvs_ = hls_ + lvap_;
00051   else if (lvap_ > 0 && hvs_ > 0) hls_ = hvs_ - lvap_;
00052   else if (hls_ > 0 && hvs_ > 0) lvap_ = hvs_ - hls_;
00053   else Process::exit(que_suis_je() + "bad parameters");
00054   return is;
00055 }
